						               													<description>A tabletop combat game system using 1.75 inch little rubber keshi figures called Nanoids. Take control of Nanoids as an Operator, your task is to close the power hungry rifts opening all over the world.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use your 6 Command cards to simultaneously activate your Nanoids in Nano Battle! Each card has a number indicating how many seconds it takes for your Nanoid to act in battle, a Dodge is almost instant while a Super move might take some time. Deplete each others Life Sparks while avoiding peril on the Nano Fields stabilizing the rifts.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Be careful, once your last Command card in hand is activated each round the rift consumes its data, never to be used in this match again. 21 total choices before you run out of commands and your Nanoid goes rogue. Can you defeat your opponent while your Nanoid is choosing its own commands?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;An expandable game system of Rumble and Nanoid Packs. Rumble Packs provide everything for 2 players to Nano Battle and can be combined or used stand-alone. Nanoid Packs add more colorful Nanoids to your arsenal of little warriors. More pack types to come such as Story and Megoids.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
